# Add the upstream JetBrains skills as a submodule:
#
#   git submodule add https://github.com/Kotlin/kotlin-agent-skills.git vendored-skills/upstream
#
# Then symlink the skills directory or point config.yaml's `skills.root`
# at vendored-skills/upstream/skills.
#
# We pin to a specific commit; phase 2.2 reads SKILL.md directly via
# --append-system-prompt-file, so a submodule bump is the only way the
# refinement prompt changes.
